WEBVTT

00:01.084 --> 00:02.294
Previously on
Cruel Summer...

00:02.294 --> 00:05.047
No pressure, but...

00:05.047 --> 00:07.132
I thought maybe
if you're ready...

00:07.132 --> 00:08.884
Yeah.

00:08.884 --> 00:10.969
-I broke up with Luke.
-You what?

00:10.969 --> 00:12.846
Isabella: One look at you
and he'll realize

00:12.846 --> 00:15.015
that what he wants
has been in front of him
this whole time.

00:17.726 --> 00:20.562
Everyone already believes
that they saw me
on that tape with Luke.

00:20.562 --> 00:23.607
-Yeah, but...
-So let's make sure
that it stays that way.

00:23.607 --> 00:26.109
Something happened
at the Plunge today.

00:26.109 --> 00:27.694
Okay, you're kind
of freaking me out.

00:27.694 --> 00:29.404
What happened?

00:29.404 --> 00:30.989
She kissed me.

00:30.989 --> 00:34.493
I can handle
both of them, no problem.

00:34.493 --> 00:36.828
Okay, I've got them
wrapped around my finger.

00:36.828 --> 00:40.999
I busted a major move
with Isabella after the Plunge,
and she couldn't get enough.

00:40.999 --> 00:42.626
Megan: He's not gonna
get away with this.

00:42.626 --> 00:44.169
Back when Luke
first disappeared,

00:44.169 --> 00:46.797
you were ready to leave town
the moment school ended.

00:46.797 --> 00:49.633
Isabella: But Debbie got sick
so I decided to stay
and help out.

00:49.633 --> 00:51.760
(computer chimes)

00:51.760 --> 00:53.595
Megan: Have you always
had those cameras,

00:53.595 --> 00:55.180
looking out towards the road?

00:55.180 --> 00:56.848
I never lied about us.

00:56.848 --> 00:59.643
I tried to be a better friend
to you than I was to Lisa.

00:59.643 --> 01:02.229
That's why I pretended to be
the one on the sex tape.

01:02.229 --> 01:06.191
Even after everything
that happened on New Year's Eve,
I had your back.

01:06.191 --> 01:10.195
Did you, or were you
just covering your ass
after what you did?

01:10.195 --> 01:13.657
I think that you went back
to the cabin on New Year's

01:13.657 --> 01:14.825
and you killed Luke.

01:16.535 --> 01:18.954
I just heard something
that I think you should know.

01:18.954 --> 01:22.457
-What are you thinking?
-I want to make Luke
wish he'd never met us.

01:22.457 --> 01:25.752
all:
Happy New Year! Whoo!

01:25.752 --> 01:27.212
(cheering)

01:27.212 --> 01:29.464
Why don't we go back
to the cabin and celebrate?

01:29.464 --> 01:31.341
Just the two of us? Hmm?

01:31.341 --> 01:33.760
Yeah, let's go.

01:35.304 --> 01:37.097
(modem beeping, buzzing)

01:55.073 --> 01:57.367
Nine Days: ♪ This is the story
of a girl... ♪

01:57.367 --> 02:00.412
It was perfect, even better
than I thought it would be.

02:00.412 --> 02:03.081
I'm so glad.

02:03.081 --> 02:05.083
Thank you.

02:05.083 --> 02:07.294
For what?

02:07.294 --> 02:09.296
Um, everything?

02:09.296 --> 02:12.424
This never would've happened
if it wasn't for you.

02:12.424 --> 02:14.051
Please.

02:14.051 --> 02:16.720
You and Luke were, like,
destined to be together.

02:16.720 --> 02:18.388
I was just your love sherpa.

02:18.388 --> 02:20.140
(Megan giggles)

02:22.934 --> 02:24.978
You're the best friend
I could ever have.

02:24.978 --> 02:26.480
I feel so lucky.

02:26.480 --> 02:28.023
Me too.

02:28.023 --> 02:30.233
(car driving up)

02:30.233 --> 02:32.986
That's him! (giggles)

02:32.986 --> 02:35.781
♪ Your hair never falls
in quite the same way ♪

02:35.781 --> 02:39.534
♪ You never seem
to run out of things to say ♪

02:39.534 --> 02:40.911
♪ This is the story ♪

02:40.911 --> 02:42.079
♪ Of a girl... ♪

02:49.294 --> 02:52.089
Wait, wait.
I wanna try something different.

02:52.089 --> 02:55.175
Different?
What do you mean, different?

02:55.175 --> 02:56.718
What? (laughing)

03:01.682 --> 03:04.309
Wow, uh...

03:04.309 --> 03:08.730
I just figured, y'know,
since the world is ending...

03:08.730 --> 03:11.483
this could be our last chance.

03:11.483 --> 03:13.110
(laughs)

03:13.110 --> 03:15.404
Whatever chatroom
gave you this idea,

03:15.404 --> 03:17.447
I offer my sincere gratitude.

03:18.824 --> 03:19.991
Come on.

03:19.991 --> 03:23.036
(keying rapidly)

03:23.036 --> 03:24.788
(computer chimes)

03:27.457 --> 03:28.959
(chimes)

03:33.463 --> 03:34.381
We need to talk.

03:38.176 --> 03:39.719
What are you doing here?

03:39.719 --> 03:41.847
