03:41.847 --> 03:43.306
He knows about our lie.

03:46.101 --> 03:47.936
(electronic squelching)

03:53.275 --> 03:54.860
Which one?

03:54.860 --> 03:56.403
That you're the one on the tape.

03:56.403 --> 03:58.363
Who told him?

03:58.363 --> 04:00.365
What, did you cut a deal
for yourself or something?

04:00.365 --> 04:03.118
No. No, the truth makes me look
just as bad as you.

04:03.118 --> 04:04.661
(sighs)

04:04.661 --> 04:06.538
Look, I don't know how
he found out,

04:06.538 --> 04:09.124
but all that matters
is that he did.

04:09.124 --> 04:11.710
Well, we have bigger problems.

04:11.710 --> 04:13.753
Steve thinks
that Ned killed Luke.

04:13.753 --> 04:15.714
He's got the cops looking
into him and everything.

04:15.714 --> 04:17.883
That just takes the heat off us,
doesn't it?

04:17.883 --> 04:19.968
Not exactly.

04:19.968 --> 04:22.971
Ned has a ton
of security cameras right
outside of his house.

04:22.971 --> 04:24.973
One of them looks out
on the road,

04:24.973 --> 04:28.477
the one that forks to his house
and the Chambers' cabin.

04:28.477 --> 04:30.353
Were they filming
on New Year's Eve?

04:30.353 --> 04:32.981
They're always filming. 24/7.

04:34.691 --> 04:36.359
If the cops find that footage...

04:36.359 --> 04:38.612
I know. That's why we have
to get it before they do.

04:38.612 --> 04:40.071
I'm headed over
to Ned's right now.

04:40.071 --> 04:41.740
Not without me you're not.

04:47.454 --> 04:49.331
(giggling)

04:49.331 --> 04:51.500
Hey, you're early.

04:51.500 --> 04:54.586
Yeah, I'm sorry,
I couldn't wait. (laughs)

04:54.586 --> 04:56.171
Cool.

04:56.171 --> 04:58.590
Uh, I'll just grab my stuff
and then I'll be ready.

04:58.590 --> 05:01.426
Um, actually, uh, Luke
and I were maybe

05:01.426 --> 05:03.303
gonna hang out for a bit
before the car wash.

05:03.303 --> 05:04.930
Upstairs.

05:04.930 --> 05:06.139
Oh.

05:06.139 --> 05:07.307
You don't mind, do you?

05:07.307 --> 05:09.768
No. No, of course not.

05:09.768 --> 05:10.894
Take your time.

05:19.861 --> 05:21.321
