-Hey.

05:25.033 --> 05:26.868
Where are Megan and Luke?

05:26.868 --> 05:28.495
I saw his car outside.

05:28.495 --> 05:29.955
They're upstairs.

05:29.955 --> 05:31.456
Oh.

05:31.456 --> 05:34.334
So are they... together now?

05:34.334 --> 05:36.127
I think so.

05:36.127 --> 05:37.921
Debbie: Ah, it's not
that big of a surprise.

05:37.921 --> 05:40.173
They've been close
since they were little.

05:42.676 --> 05:43.844
You doing okay?

05:43.844 --> 05:45.929
Yeah.

05:45.929 --> 05:48.306
Yeah, of course.
I'm really happy for them.

05:48.306 --> 05:49.724
I just, um...

05:49.724 --> 05:51.476
don't totally know
where I fit in.

05:51.476 --> 05:53.687
Right alongside Megan still.

05:53.687 --> 05:55.480
Plus, school's starting soon.

05:55.480 --> 05:58.817
Yeah. Yeah, you're right,
I'm excited.

05:58.817 --> 06:01.152
Not about the homework part,
but, um...

06:01.152 --> 06:04.573
the football games,
the pep rallies--

06:04.573 --> 06:06.825
