at boarding school.

06:06.825 --> 06:08.994
I'm guessing no car wash either.

06:08.994 --> 06:10.412
Nope.

06:10.412 --> 06:13.248
You should head over.
See what it's all about.

06:13.248 --> 06:14.541
I think I will.

06:15.959 --> 06:17.502
Hey.

06:17.502 --> 06:19.337
Listen, you're gonna have
a terrific senior year.

06:25.093 --> 06:26.970
Steve Chambers
has been all over me.

06:26.970 --> 06:29.097
He's convinced Ned Faunce
killed Luke.

06:29.097 --> 06:31.224
I'm not sure
I'm buying it, but...

06:31.224 --> 06:33.894
there's definitely something
going on between him
and Megan Landry.

06:33.894 --> 06:36.771
Think it's criminal?

06:36.771 --> 06:38.732
Well, six months ago
I would've said no.

06:38.732 --> 06:40.901
But now I wouldn't
put anything past her.

06:40.901 --> 06:44.487
Or Isabella.
They've been lying
about the sex tape for months.

06:44.487 --> 06:47.407
Puts a whole new light
on their relationship,
on all their statements.

06:49.826 --> 06:52.746
Have you finished going through
Jeff Pope's footage
from the party?

06:52.746 --> 06:55.081
Still in it. Uh...

06:55.081 --> 06:57.584
