worth mentioning with the girls.

06:57.584 --> 06:59.336
Yeah, keep looking.

06:59.336 --> 07:01.963
If they've conspired
about the tape all this time,

07:01.963 --> 07:03.506
who knows what else
they're hiding?

07:17.771 --> 07:23.526
♪ There's something there
beside me ♪

07:23.526 --> 07:26.738
♪ There's something
that I see ♪

07:29.366 --> 07:33.620
♪ I left
the engine running... ♪

07:33.620 --> 07:35.997
I used to think it would be
so weird, kissing you.

07:35.997 --> 07:37.666
