07:37.666 --> 07:39.668
Dude, I've seen you in diapers.

07:39.668 --> 07:41.503
Yeah, when I was, like, two.

07:41.503 --> 07:43.254
Well, yeah. Thank God.

07:43.254 --> 07:45.757
(giggling) No!

07:47.759 --> 07:48.968
