07:48.968 --> 07:51.638
it's not weird at all.

07:51.638 --> 07:54.057
Actually, it kinda makes it--

07:54.057 --> 07:55.642
Better?

07:55.642 --> 07:57.102
Yeah.

07:57.102 --> 07:59.020
Like...

07:59.020 --> 08:02.273
I know pretty much
everything about you,

08:02.273 --> 08:05.735
but there's still stuff
that's...

08:05.735 --> 08:08.321
Uncharted territory?

08:08.321 --> 08:09.531
Uh-huh.

08:11.866 --> 08:14.327
And I want to explore...

08:14.327 --> 08:16.162
all of that.

08:16.162 --> 08:17.330
With you.

08:19.374 --> 08:21.042
I like the sound of that.

08:25.004 --> 08:28.425
Gosh...
I'm so glad that I waited,

08:28.425 --> 08:30.635
you know, that we get
to be each other's first.

08:30.635 --> 08:32.470
It's gonna make it
so much more special.

08:32.470 --> 08:34.013
Don't you think?

08:37.308 --> 08:39.561
Yeah, I do.

08:39.561 --> 08:44.357
♪ How many times
have we been through? ♪

08:46.443 --> 08:48.862
♪ Is this where we find... ♪

08:51.656 --> 08:54.034
I don't know what I did
to deserve this.

08:54.034 --> 08:56.411
So many things.

09:07.881 --> 09:09.299
I'm starting to get goosebumps.

09:09.299 --> 09:12.635
Hmm. About to have
a lot more than that.

09:12.635 --> 09:14.095
(straining)

09:16.848 --> 09:20.810
Should we have, like...
should we have a safe word?

09:20.810 --> 09:22.979
What's that?

09:22.979 --> 09:25.190
It's like, uh,
it's a word that you pick

09:25.190 --> 09:29.277
so that, you know, if things
start getting too intense

09:29.277 --> 09:32.906
and someone wants to stop,
you can say it.

09:32.906 --> 09:35.408
Like...
something like "Lasagna."

09:35.408 --> 09:37.077
How about...

09:38.453 --> 09:39.913
"Control-alt-delete"?

09:41.498 --> 09:43.958
(laughs) You got it.

09:43.958 --> 09:45.335
I'll try to be gentle.

09:45.335 --> 09:47.212
