09:47.212 --> 09:48.922
Ooh.

09:48.922 --> 09:51.007
(groaning softly)

09:51.007 --> 09:52.926
It's kinda tight.

09:52.926 --> 09:55.512
Hmm. Don't want you escaping.

09:55.512 --> 09:57.013
Just try to relax.

10:06.481 --> 10:07.732
