10:12.070 --> 10:14.364
-Whoo!
-(car horn blares)

10:14.364 --> 10:16.032
(intense music playing)

10:20.203 --> 10:22.247
Parker:
Hey, boys.

10:22.247 --> 10:25.250
Jeff: All right, all right.
This is our senior
kickoff event.

10:25.250 --> 10:26.835
Tell everybody
what it's about.

10:26.835 --> 10:28.586
Washing cars, yo!

10:28.586 --> 10:30.755
