we rule the school!

10:30.755 --> 10:32.549
-Whoo!
-Yay!

10:32.549 --> 10:34.050
Leave the dirty work to us

10:34.050 --> 10:36.761
and come support
the class of 2000!

10:36.761 --> 10:39.347
-(cheering)
-We're wet and wild!

10:39.347 --> 10:41.808
Hey! Yo, Isabella,
you wanna get wet?

10:41.808 --> 10:45.603
