10:51.609 --> 10:53.695
Wow, Tim and his limp hose.

10:53.695 --> 10:55.446
-Ooh!
-Come on,
let's get you a bucket.

10:55.446 --> 10:57.824
-Watch out, bro...
-Bye.

10:57.824 --> 10:59.242
girl:
Hey, guys!

10:59.242 --> 11:03.705
