and your versions don't line up.

12:23.785 --> 12:25.662
I love you guys.

12:25.662 --> 12:28.206
I just want to know the truth
so we can all move forward.

12:28.206 --> 12:29.874
Okay, well, are you gonna
tie her up too?

12:29.874 --> 12:31.584
I'm sure you'd love that,
wouldn't you?

12:33.461 --> 12:34.671
Damn it!

12:34.671 --> 12:36.172
Isabella:
Stop fighting, Luke.

12:36.172 --> 12:38.341
