13:20.133 --> 13:21.884
-Guys, seriously,
it's not funny.
-Voilà.

13:21.884 --> 13:23.845
-Truth serum.
-Luke: Please.

13:23.845 --> 13:27.181
And liquid courage for us.

13:27.181 --> 13:29.976
Luke: Okay? Look,
it's not funny anymore.

13:29.976 --> 13:31.311
