13:48.953 --> 13:50.288
Luke:
Come on!

13:51.789 --> 13:52.749
There.

13:54.208 --> 13:56.002
You gotta be kidding me.

13:56.002 --> 13:57.336
(Megan sighs)

14:06.179 --> 14:08.264
