14:53.434 --> 14:55.812
I think I remember
how his fingers moved.

14:55.812 --> 14:58.022
(alarm chirps)

14:58.022 --> 14:59.941
Isabella:
Impressive.

15:04.403 --> 15:05.738
Okay, this way.

15:14.205 --> 15:17.250
(sighs) I don't know how
he labelled the outside cameras
or where he put them.

15:17.250 --> 15:19.585
They're not in the same folder
as the interior ones.

15:19.585 --> 15:22.255
Well, yeah.

15:22.255 --> 15:24.465
I mean, I'm just saying,
if I were hella paranoid,

15:24.465 --> 15:26.300
