to be way more creepy.

15:46.362 --> 15:48.948
(keying continues)

15:48.948 --> 15:51.534
Why'd you, um...

15:51.534 --> 15:53.578
Why'd you hide your...

15:53.578 --> 15:55.538
whatever it was with Ned?

15:55.538 --> 15:58.499
