a place to be comparing secrets?

16:00.960 --> 16:02.086
(stops keying)

16:04.714 --> 16:07.633
When I first started
working with Ned,

16:07.633 --> 16:09.969
the tape had just happened

16:09.969 --> 16:13.848
and me and you were at eleven,
like, all the time.

16:15.474 --> 16:17.226
It was...

16:17.226 --> 16:19.145
it was a lot.

16:19.145 --> 16:21.439
I think that...

16:21.439 --> 16:24.984
