that was just mine.

16:24.984 --> 16:26.152
Separate.

16:26.152 --> 16:27.403
Yeah.

16:29.572 --> 16:31.991
I would've let you have it.

16:31.991 --> 16:33.618
Or...

16:33.618 --> 16:36.162
whatever, but...

16:36.162 --> 16:38.706
lying about it
made it so much worse.

16:44.962 --> 16:46.756
Oh, here we go.
I think I found something.

16:46.756 --> 16:47.924
