friends your own age to harass?

32:50.969 --> 32:52.637
Nice sass.

32:52.637 --> 32:54.556
Yeah, but, uh...

32:54.556 --> 32:56.975
Now that you're done with Luke,
I was just thinking

32:56.975 --> 33:00.228
maybe you wanna upgrade,

33:00.228 --> 33:02.522
take a spin
on the OG Chambers bro?

33:02.522 --> 33:03.773
I'd rather eat glass.

33:06.568 --> 33:08.737
-(chuckles)
-You're a jerk!

33:08.737 --> 33:10.739
Oh, come on,
you know that you want it.

33:10.739 --> 33:12.741
Not in any universe.

33:12.741 --> 33:15.452
Okay, well, you're there
tossing it around,

33:15.452 --> 33:17.996
okay, you're asking for it.

33:17.996 --> 33:20.373
You're a tease.

33:20.373 --> 33:21.416
And you're a pathetic asshole.

33:24.169 --> 33:25.420
(car alarm chirps)

33:27.255 --> 33:29.132
Where's he going?

33:29.132 --> 33:31.134
You all right?

33:31.134 --> 33:32.969
He likes to push
the envelope, huh?

33:32.969 --> 33:34.971
He's totally harmless.

33:34.971 --> 33:36.514
Boys will be boys, right?

33:38.308 --> 33:39.476
You're okay.

33:45.857 --> 33:48.151
(R&B playing)

33:53.573 --> 33:56.201
-Hey.
-How's it going?

33:56.201 --> 33:59.204
My fingers are starting
to pucker. (giggles)

34:00.914 --> 34:03.041
-You okay?
-Yeah.

34:05.043 --> 34:06.544
You sure?

34:06.544 --> 34:08.546
You seem a little off.

34:08.546 --> 34:11.174
I'm just dehydrated.

34:11.174 --> 34:13.510
Okay. If you say so.

34:13.510 --> 34:15.637
You'd tell me if something
was wrong, right?

34:15.637 --> 34:17.347
Of course.

34:17.347 --> 34:18.515
No secrets.

34:22.018 --> 34:24.187
Well, I think Luke and I are
probably gonna bounce soon.

34:24.187 --> 34:26.231
So, I'll see you later?

34:26.231 --> 34:27.190
Okay.

34:33.488 --> 34:36.199
Can you run me through
what you did after the party
one more time?

34:36.199 --> 34:38.451
You have my client's
statement on this.

34:38.451 --> 34:39.411
Humor me.

34:45.041 --> 34:46.751
Luke and I went to the cabin.

34:46.751 --> 34:48.712
We hung out for a while

34:48.712 --> 34:51.381
and then I left him there,
went home.

34:51.381 --> 34:54.301
The next day when I went back
to take him to the train,
he was gone.

34:54.301 --> 34:58.430
I wasn't feeling well, so I left
the party early, went to bed.

34:58.430 --> 35:00.432
When did you last see Megan?

35:00.432 --> 35:02.309
I guess the next day.

35:02.309 --> 35:04.394
And when was the last time
you saw Isabella that night?

35:04.394 --> 35:05.312
At the party.

35:07.439 --> 35:10.734
This is Jeff Pope's footage
from the party.

35:10.734 --> 35:12.986
We went through it
when Luke went missing,

35:12.986 --> 35:15.989
searching for clues to
as why he might have run away.

35:15.989 --> 35:19.618
Based upon what we now know,
a second watch was...

35:19.618 --> 35:21.202
enlightening.

35:21.202 --> 35:25.999
(crowd clamoring)

35:25.999 --> 35:27.626
Rebecca:
What are we watching here?

35:27.626 --> 35:30.587
It's not so much what we see,
it's what we hear.

35:30.587 --> 35:34.633
It took some doing,
but our tech was able
to isolate your conversation.

35:34.633 --> 35:37.260
Megan: No, I'm not going
to let him get away with this.

35:37.260 --> 35:39.512
I'm not gonna
let him off that easy.

35:39.512 --> 35:41.765
What are you thinking?

35:41.765 --> 35:44.559
I think we should get
some serious revenge.

35:44.559 --> 35:46.478
I want to make Luke wish
that he'd never met us.

35:47.854 --> 35:49.648
Isabella:
What's your plan?

35:49.648 --> 35:52.233
-(video stops)
-Friends, co-conspirators.

35:52.233 --> 35:54.402
Call it what you like,
but you were clearly plotting

35:54.402 --> 35:56.655
against Luke on New Year's Eve.

35:56.655 --> 35:58.406
Together.

36:02.202 --> 36:03.953
You had sex with Luke?

36:07.123 --> 36:08.958
Megan, look...

36:08.958 --> 36:10.502
-I wanted to tell you.
-Luke: Megan...

36:10.502 --> 36:12.712
No, I wanted to tell you, okay?

36:12.712 --> 36:14.798
But he told me
not to say anything.

36:14.798 --> 36:16.716
He said that it would
hurt you too much.

36:16.716 --> 36:18.510
No, no, no, she said that you

36:18.510 --> 36:21.179
were too insecure to handle it.

36:21.179 --> 36:22.931
Isabella:
That's bullshit!

36:22.931 --> 36:26.643
No! No, you told me that
she wouldn't get over it!

36:26.643 --> 36:30.980
Megan, I didn't want to ruin
things with you, so I
went along with it, I swear.

36:30.980 --> 36:33.692
Because keeping a secret
with my boyfriend

36:33.692 --> 36:36.277
while I walk around clueless
wouldn't do any damage?

36:36.277 --> 36:38.113
-Megan!
-Don't. Don't.

36:38.113 --> 36:39.989
-Isabella.
-Megan, Megan, I'm sorry.

36:39.989 --> 36:42.117
Look at me, please.
I'm sorry, okay?

36:42.117 --> 36:44.452
Look, I thought
I was protecting you.

36:44.452 --> 36:48.415
I thought you were
my best friend, my sister.

36:48.415 --> 36:49.874
What a joke!

36:49.874 --> 36:51.584
-Megan, talk to me.
-No.

36:51.584 --> 36:53.253
No, we can talk this out,
okay, we can.

36:53.253 --> 36:55.672
Don't let her come
in between us.

36:55.672 --> 36:57.132
Screw you, Luke!

36:57.132 --> 36:59.592
No. Look...

36:59.592 --> 37:03.596
You always say how possessive
she is, right, how smothering?

37:05.849 --> 37:08.810
Look, she's gonna say anything
that she can right now.

37:08.810 --> 37:10.854
I mean, we...
we can talk this out, okay?

37:10.854 --> 37:13.481
We can, we can together, okay?
Okay?

37:13.481 --> 37:16.109
Look, I know I screwed up,
I know.

37:16.109 --> 37:19.612
I would not intentionally
hurt you, you know that.

37:19.612 --> 37:21.740
I wouldn't do it.
I love you.

37:21.740 --> 37:23.533
Shut up! (cocks gun)

37:30.165 --> 37:32.041
(relaxing music playing)

37:36.087 --> 37:38.840
Do they really think they're
being, like, stealth?

37:38.840 --> 37:41.301
(laughs) Maybe.

37:41.301 --> 37:43.011
I don't know,
but they suck at it.

37:43.011 --> 37:45.472
Debbie:
(laughing) Steve!

37:45.472 --> 37:47.849
Oh, my dad's kind of always
had a thing for your mom,

37:47.849 --> 37:50.477
so I'm not, like, shocked.

37:50.477 --> 37:52.979
Yeah, still, it's...

37:52.979 --> 37:57.066
He's her boss. It's...
It's a bad idea, in every way.

37:57.066 --> 38:00.403
Okay, go with me on this.

38:01.946 --> 38:03.573
If they're happy...

38:03.573 --> 38:05.158
(Debbie laughing)

38:05.158 --> 38:07.452
...and, I'm sorry, but those
are not unhappy noises--

38:07.452 --> 38:09.579
Eww! Gross.

38:09.579 --> 38:12.165
I'm just saying...

38:12.165 --> 38:13.708
then they'll get off our backs.

38:16.085 --> 38:19.631
And then "family time"
will mean that...

38:19.631 --> 38:21.925
we just get to be together.

38:21.925 --> 38:25.345
So, it's kind of a win-win.

38:25.345 --> 38:28.389
Okay. There is some logic there.

38:28.389 --> 38:30.433
It's creepy,
but it might be sound.

38:30.433 --> 38:32.060
See? I'm a genius.

38:32.060 --> 38:34.229
And what happens
if they break up, Einstein?

38:34.229 --> 38:35.563
What then?

38:35.563 --> 38:38.900
(clicks tongue)
Well, that would be ugly.

38:42.612 --> 38:44.531
When Megan saw this,
she admitted that

38:44.531 --> 38:47.075
you were with her and Luke
at the cabin after the party.

38:47.075 --> 38:49.410
That proves nothing.

38:49.410 --> 38:51.246
It's her word against
my client's.

38:51.246 --> 38:53.248
You may recall,
the toxicology indicated

38:53.248 --> 38:55.875
the presence of benzodiazepines
in Luke's system

38:55.875 --> 38:58.753
at the time of his death.

38:58.753 --> 39:00.922
She also accused you
of bringing pills to the cabin

39:00.922 --> 39:02.549
and drugging Luke.

39:02.549 --> 39:04.968
Tom:
You don't need to answer that.

39:04.968 --> 39:08.471
He's just fishing.

39:08.471 --> 39:11.015
I'd advise you
to tell me everything you can

39:11.015 --> 39:12.517
about what Isabella did

39:12.517 --> 39:16.271
and what Megan did that night
at the cabin.

39:16.271 --> 39:19.232
Unless you want to go down
for this...

39:19.232 --> 39:20.817
alone.

39:24.654 --> 39:27.240
(The Cardigans
playing "Lovefool")

39:27.240 --> 39:31.494
♪ Dear, I fear
we're facing a problem ♪

39:31.494 --> 39:35.540
♪ You love me
no longer, I know ♪

39:35.540 --> 39:40.712
♪ And maybe there is
nothing that I can do ♪

39:40.712 --> 39:44.173
♪ To make you do ♪

39:44.173 --> 39:48.428
♪ Mama tells me
I shouldn't bother ♪

39:48.428 --> 39:52.932
♪ That I ought to stick
to another man... ♪

39:52.932 --> 39:54.767
Hey!

39:54.767 --> 39:56.811
-What are you doing?
-Looking for you.

39:56.811 --> 39:59.439
-We wanted to figure out
what to do tonight.
-Oh.

39:59.439 --> 40:01.024
-Cool.
-What are you up for?

40:01.024 --> 40:02.150
You always have the best ideas.

40:04.110 --> 40:05.695
Absolutely anything.

40:05.695 --> 40:07.155
♪ Love me, love me... ♪

40:07.155 --> 40:09.532
Stick with what we discussed
and that's it.

40:13.411 --> 40:15.038
I'm ready when you are.

40:19.292 --> 40:21.836
Yes, Isabella
was with me and Luke

40:21.836 --> 40:24.881
at the cabin on New Year's Eve.

40:24.881 --> 40:28.635
We wanted to confront Luke
for talking trash about us.

40:28.635 --> 40:30.637
But everything that happened
that night...

40:30.637 --> 40:31.930
...was her fault.

40:31.930 --> 40:33.389
Including Luke's death.

40:33.389 --> 40:36.059
Including
Luke's death.

40:36.059 --> 40:37.852
Megan: What are you doing?
Isabella, put it down!

40:37.852 --> 40:39.520
-Now!
-Are you insane?!

40:39.520 --> 40:40.772
Oh, my God!

40:40.772 --> 40:42.231
Take back what you said.

40:42.231 --> 40:44.275
-Megan--
-Take it back, Luke!

40:44.275 --> 40:46.110
She's literally crazy.

40:46.110 --> 40:50.657
No. No, tell Megan
that I'm a great friend!

40:50.657 --> 40:53.242
Tell her that you made me lie,
that I didn't want to do it!

40:53.242 --> 40:54.619
You made me, Luke. Tell her!

40:54.619 --> 40:56.120
Isabella, stop! Please.

40:56.120 --> 40:58.206
Then you see that she's crazy.
She's crazy.

40:58.206 --> 41:00.917
Megan, please.
Megan, don't listen to him!

41:00.917 --> 41:02.377
I know, it's okay.

41:02.377 --> 41:04.462
It's okay,
just put it down. Okay?

41:04.462 --> 41:06.881
Isabella, what do you want?
You want Megan all to yourself?

41:06.881 --> 41:08.967
-Is that what this is?
-Luke, shut up!

41:08.967 --> 41:11.052
Megan, you and I have known
each other our entire lives.

41:11.052 --> 41:14.013
We have. She's only been...

41:14.013 --> 41:17.141
You've only been here
for a minute, okay,
and you're gonna be gone soon.

41:17.141 --> 41:19.227
She's gonna forget you,
she's not gonna pick your side,

41:19.227 --> 41:21.521
so why don't you just...
just put the gun down?

41:25.692 --> 41:27.527
(Megan screams)

41:30.029 --> 41:31.698
(theme song playing)
